Params: {2: 'Electronic Voice:', 3: 'Message has been sent via the nearest relay point.'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'Looks like this will be my last message.'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'But at least my "Tempest" has reached you, right?'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'Ayla, I once told you why I wanted to become a Construct...'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: '"Our paths would be rectified if we could portray the world as it truly is."'}
{2: 'Selena', 3: "I'm sorry, Ayla. I chose my own path without letting you know..."}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'Even when I know we are so similar.'}
{3: "Another Corrupted falls to the ground from Selena's attack."}
{2: 'Selena', 3: 'I always feel that you are next to me, fighting together.'}
